        datacite:description   "Presentation held at the Data Stewardship Knowledge Exchange Event at EMBL-Heidelberg in May 2026 about the implementation of Data Stewardship at NFDI4BIOIMAGE.\n\n \n\nWe acknowledge funding by the Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG, German Research Foundation) under the National Research Data Infrastructure – NFDI 46/1 – 501864659.";
