        datacite:creator       orcid:0000-0002-4101-6987;
        datacite:description   "In this workshop the participants get an introduction to OMERO and its core concepts (projects, datasets, images, metadata, permissions). Additionally they perform a few hands-on tasks: OMERO functionalities, data annotation using a REMBI table, and OMERO.figure.\n\nThis workshop was part of the FDM-Werkstatt 2026 in Düsseldorf.\n\n ";
        datacite:resourceType  "Interactive resource";
        datacite:right         "None" , "Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International";
        datacite:title         "[Workshop] Imaging data management with OMERO - Hands-on - by Vanessa Fuchs | NFDI4BIOIMAGE" .

