        datacite:description   "The poster presents the consortium NFDI4BIOIMAGE with its objectives, key achievements until February 2026 and the support offered by its data stewardship team and help desk service. We recommend strategies to make bioimage data FAIRer along the individual stages of the research data life cycle.  \n\nVersion 2 additionally comprises the poster in svg format for more flexible reuse.\n\n\n\n\n\nThe consortium NFDI4BIOIMAGE is funded by DFG grant number NFDI 46/1, project number 501864659.";
        datacite:resourceType  "Poster";
        datacite:right         "None" , "Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International";
        datacite:title         "[2026 GerBI Community Meeting] NFDI4BIOIMAGE and its Help Desk for Community Support in Bioimage Research Data Management" .

