        datacite:description   "Presentation slides from RDM4Mic 2025. The pdf slides give an overview of various (meta)data integration activities including OMERO and ARC Interoperability, OMERO and 3D Slicer integration via plugin and OME-Zarr and 3D Slicer plugin to read imaging data from S3 bucket. The presentation is available on RDM4Mic channel on YouTube.";
        datacite:resourceType  "Presentation";
